title: Unique 2 Bed 1 Bath w/ Tons of Closet Space & Updated Kitchen!
posting_body: ['Taluswood is the perfect place to call home.', 'Convenient yet quiet location, close to i5, 10-minute walk away from QFC, and just minutes away from the Mountlake Terrace transit center.', '2 Bedroom, 1 Bath  884Sq Ft', 'A quietly cozy one-bedroom home, surrounded by lush greenery and in a convenient location Including fireplace with mantel; washer & dryer in home; large bedroom with spacious closets; & plenty of outdoor storage, self cleaning oven; modern lighting in your roomy kitchen, which includes a garbage disposal; dishwasher, and a large refrigerator.', ' This kitchen has lots of counter space, drawers and outlets.', 'We are pre-wired for cable, phone and internet access.', 'Facilities:', 'Pool, 24hr Fitness center, Playground, Barbecue, Tennis court, Basketball court, 1/4th Mile Long Lighted Walking Trail, Dog Walking Stations.', 'Parking: Covered', 'Parking notes: Required $45 monthly parking for covered/reserved parking', 'Security and Access: Disability access', 'We are pet friendly:', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Call Leasing Consultant for details.', '•$30 Monthly Pet Rent •$200 refundable deposit •$300 non-refundable fee •60lb Weight Limit •2 Pet Limit', 'Leasing Info.', 'Deposit: $250 refundable security deposit', 'Application fee: $20 per adult + $300 Admin Fee per apartment', 'Notes: call / email to schedule a tour!', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday – Friday: 10:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday:', '10:00am to 5:00pm', 'Sunday:', '10:00am to 5:00pm', 'Professionally managed by Security Properties Residential', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Taluswood Apartments', 'Check us out at: <URL>', 'P:', 'show contact info', '4208 236th St SW', 'Mountlake Terrace, WA 98043', '<URL>', 'SPRCL78']
